  "description": "Tests ability to find patients across the autoimmune disease umbrella. Per PheKB algorithm, this phenotype combines 51 autoimmune diseases under a single classification \u2014 testing whether LLM understands 'autoimmune' as a category spanning rheumatology, GI, neurology, endocrinology, dermatology.",
